    thinking: "**Eliminating AI Generation**\n\nI\'ve decided to proceed by removing the AI generation functionality. I\'m starting by addressing the `onStart` event in `App.tsx` and the related generating state views. Next, I\'ll delete the unused `/src/components/Generating` file. This should effectively remove the AI-driven aspects of the application as requested.\n\n\n**Deleting Unused Files**\n\nI\'m removing more unused files. I\'ve deleted `/src/game/beatmap.ts` as it\'s no longer necessary. Now I\'m moving on to updating the UI and color scheme, including changes to `index.html` to set the language to zh-TW. I am also planning on removing the generation section and adding a red star icon, and translating labels into Chinese within Menu.tsx. I am considering a background of `bg-zinc-950` with accents of `red-600`.\n\n\n**Refining Note Colors**\n\nI\'m now focusing on the visual changes. I\'m leaning toward using Red and White notes. I\'m updating the `COLOR_MAP` accordingly and translating \"STAGE CLEARED,\" \"Max Combo,\" \"Accuracy,\" \"Perfect,\" \"Great,\" \"Good,\" and \"Miss\" within `Result.tsx` into Traditional Chinese. I\'m also removing the audio generation download button as it\'s no longer relevant, and reviewing the role of the beatmap download function. Lastly, I will be updating `App.tsx` by removing the `Generating`, `audioService`, and `beatmap` imports, and the `generating` state.\n\n\n"
